snippet.title: RGX Showdown Reveal Trailer
snippet.description: It’s you against the world as you race through traffic in teeth-gritting, edge-of-your-seat street races. Be a part of hourly, online tournaments where you go one-on-one with opponents from all over the globe. Climb the ranks, unlock cars and customizations, and claim your championship title.
